  "prompt": "Are there any creams which help me to gain weight?",
  "response": "There are no topical creams that can help you gain weight. Weight gain typically occurs through the intake of calories and nutrients, which are processed by your digestive system. If you're looking to gain weight, consider increasing your intake of high-calorie, nutrient-dense foods such as nuts, seeds, avocados, lean meats, dairy products, and whole grains. Additionally, strength training exercises can help you build muscle mass, which can contribute to weight gain.\n\nIt's always a good idea to consult with a healthcare provider or a nutritionist to develop a plan that's tailored to your specific needs and health conditions.",
